description=
description=A thick, terrifying fog rolls across Kentucky... and they are coming.
description=Inspired by the classic mod "The Darkness Is Coming," The Fog Descend introduces a terrifying, periodic world event that transforms Project Zomboid into a fight for survival against a highly aggressive, hyper-alert horde.
description=
description=When the air raid sirens sound, a thick, heavy fog rolls over the map, severely limiting your visibility. But the dark veil is only the beginning: the zombies are responsive to the fog, becoming faster, stronger, and relentlessly aggressive. 
description=
description=Feature List
description= Dynamic Weather Event: A thick, desaturated fog sets in periodically, bringing a dark, tense atmosphere to your world.
description= Air Raid Sirens: Hear the ominous sound of distant sirens signaling the approach of the fog.
description= Sprinter Mutation: For the duration of the event, normal zombies morph into deadly sprinters with enhanced sight and hearing.
description= Vehicle Malfunctions: The electromagnetic density of the fog interferes with vehicle electronics. Driving through the fog carries a persistent risk of engine sputtering and sudden stalls, leaving you stranded in the open.
description=Requirements
description=This mod requires Living World Framework to schedule events and handle zombie modifiers safely.
